arguments.template:
<ng-container [ngSwitch]="isEdited">
            <ng-content *ngSwitchCase="false"></ng-content>
            <ng-container *ngSwitchCase="true">
                <template
                    *ngIf="column.editTemplateRef"
                    [ngTemplateOutlet]="column.editTemplateRef"
                    [ngOutletContext]="{
                        $implicit: formGroup,
                        isNew: isNew,
                        column: column,
                        dataItem: dataItem,
                        formGroup: formGroup,
                        rowIndex: rowIndex
                    }">
                </template>
                <ng-container [ngSwitch]="column.editor" *ngIf="!column.editTemplate">
                    <input
                        *ngSwitchCase="'numeric'"
                        type="number"
                        class="k-textbox"
                        [formControl]="formGroup.get(column.field)"
                    />

                    <input
                        *ngSwitchCase="'date'"
                        type="date"
                        class="k-textbox"
                        [formControl]="formGroup.get(column.field)"
                    />

                    <input
                        *ngSwitchCase="'boolean'"
                        type="checkbox"
                        [formControl]="formGroup.get(column.field)"
                    />

                    <input
                        *ngSwitchDefault
                        type="text"
                        class="k-textbox"
                        [formControl]="formGroup.get(column.field)"
                    />
                </ng-container>
            </ng-container>
        </ng-container>
